author: @user-es4cm1pz4e
content:
A strong person, experience that cannot be denied.

Everyone will always be speaking about Madonna, whether you love her or not, and that’s why she and her music are more alive than always. I’m glad that I can see her going strong, it’s a privilege if you know the meaning of music and an artist.
